WEBVTT

00:01.831 --> 00:03.084
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:03.084 --> 00:03.964
AGENT REBECCA STONE,
HOMELAND SECURITY.

00:03.964 --> 00:05.126
I'VE BEEN UNDERCOVER

00:05.126 --> 00:06.217
BUILDING A CASE
AGAINST THE GRAYSONS --

00:06.217 --> 00:07.218
YOU'LL WEAR THIS WIRE.

00:07.218 --> 00:08.339
WE'LL WATCH YOUR EVERY MOVE

00:08.339 --> 00:09.840
UNTIL YOU GET A CONFESSION
FROM CONRAD.

00:09.840 --> 00:12.223
I THINK PASCAL IS TALKING
TO HOMELAND SECURITY.

00:12.223 --> 00:14.765
THE ONLY PERSON HE HAS
TO OFFER UP IS DAD, RIGHT?

00:14.765 --> 00:17.308
PASCAL HAS BEEN
TALKING TO THE FEDS.

00:17.308 --> 00:18.729
PASCAL...

00:18.729 --> 00:19.560
WATCH OUT!

00:19.560 --> 00:20.731
[ THUD, SQUISH ]

00:20.731 --> 00:21.982
I TRIED TO WARN HIM,
BUT IT WAS TOO LATE.

00:21.982 --> 00:24.024
NO, NO!

00:24.024 --> 00:25.566
WHO WROTE THIS?
 I HAVE A GUESS.

00:25.566 --> 00:27.198
IT CAN'T BE DAVID CLARKE.

00:27.198 --> 00:29.200
DIGITAL STAMP
FROM A LOCAL POST OFFICE

00:29.200 --> 00:30.781
AND TRACKS TO...

00:30.781 --> 00:32.613
A CABIN IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE BERKSHIRES.

00:32.613 --> 00:35.416
SO, THIS REALLY IS JUST SOME
SICKO TRYING TO MESS WITH ME.

00:35.416 --> 00:37.118
LET'S GO
BEFORE HE COMES HOME.

00:42.293 --> 00:44.335
[ GASPS, SOBS ]

00:46.797 --> 00:49.090
[ SCREAMING ]

00:49.090 --> 00:51.011
Emily: SEIZED...

00:51.011 --> 00:52.553
CONFINED...

00:52.553 --> 00:54.225
CAPTIVE.

00:54.225 --> 00:57.478
SIX YEARS OF MY YOUTH
 WERE SPENT THAT WAY.

01:01.392 --> 01:04.144
NO!
 [ Distorted ]
COOPERATE AND YOU'LL BE FINE.

01:04.144 --> 01:06.527
IN JUVENILE DETENTION,
 MANY LOST HOPE.

01:08.028 --> 01:12.243
FOR ME, BEING LOCKED AWAY
 WAS AN IMPETUS FOR REVENGE

01:12.243 --> 01:14.405
AND FOR THE VOW
 THAT ONCE I GOT OUT,

01:14.405 --> 01:17.408
I WOULD PUNISH THOSE
 WHO TOOK MY FREEDOM.

01:20.581 --> 01:22.123
DID YOU GET IT?

01:22.123 --> 01:23.124
[ CHARLOTTE SOBBING ]

01:23.124 --> 01:24.795
[ CAMERA BEEPS ]

01:24.795 --> 01:26.337
EVERYTHING WE NEED.

01:26.337 --> 01:28.419
[ SOBS ]

01:32.213 --> 01:34.265
[ GULLS CRYING ]

01:43.814 --> 01:46.777
REMEMBER WHEN I USED TO DRAG YOU
HERE AS A LITTLE BOY

01:46.777 --> 01:48.859
TO GO BIRD-WATCHING?

01:48.859 --> 01:50.991
YOU HATED IT.

01:50.991 --> 01:53.494
I ACTUALLY LOVED
THOSE TIMES, MOM.

01:53.494 --> 01:55.366
AH.

01:55.366 --> 01:58.078
WELL, ENJOY THEIR SONGS
WHILE YOU CAN, DANIEL.

01:58.078 --> 02:01.872
THEY'LL SOON BE TAKING OFF
FOR WARMER WEATHER.

02:04.665 --> 02:07.047
EVERYONE LEAVES.

02:08.878 --> 02:11.592
PASCAL DIDN'T CHOOSE
TO GO.

02:16.096 --> 02:20.221
[ Voice breaking ]
I STILL CAN'T GET THE HORROR
OF LAST NIGHT OUT OF MY HEAD.

02:22.523 --> 02:25.316
CONRAD WILL PAY
FOR WHAT HE'S DONE,

02:25.316 --> 02:26.977
AS WILL EMILY THORNE.

02:28.189 --> 02:30.361
WHY DO YOU THINK
 SHE WAS INVOLVED?

02:30.361 --> 02:33.444
JUST BEFORE HE WENT
WITH YOUR FATHER ON THE ROOF,

02:33.444 --> 02:35.326
PASCAL SHARED A LOOK
WITH EMILY,

02:35.326 --> 02:37.778
AND IT WAS AS IF SHE WAS
ORDERING HIM THERE.

02:39.159 --> 02:41.121
YEAH,
THE HOMELAND SECURITY AGENT

02:41.121 --> 02:44.375
THAT PASCAL WAS WORKING WITH
WAS A WOMAN.

02:44.375 --> 02:46.917
A GHOST WHOSE NUMBER
HAS BEEN DISCONNECTED.

02:48.168 --> 02:49.460
YEAH, I'LL LOOK INTO IT.

02:49.460 --> 02:52.002
IN THE MEANTIME,
YOU NEED TO GET HOME,

02:52.002 --> 02:53.294
GET SOME REST.

02:53.294 --> 02:56.006
SLEEP CAN WAIT, DANIEL.

02:58.599 --> 03:01.262
I HAVE VERMIN TO STALK.

03:02.893 --> 03:05.976
Margaux: THANKS FOR MEETING
WITH ME, DETECTIVE.

03:05.976 --> 03:09.980
MY FAMILY AND I ARE IN SHOCK
AND DESPERATE FOR DETAILS.

03:11.151 --> 03:14.655
I WAS HOPING
YOU COULD SHARE YOUR FINDINGS.

03:14.655 --> 03:17.027
HERE'S WHAT I GOT --
UH, THE TWO EYEWITNESSES,

03:17.027 --> 03:19.119
CONRAD GRAYSON
AND THE HELICOPTER PILOT,

03:19.119 --> 03:20.491
WERE QUESTIONED
LAST NIGHT.

03:20.491 --> 03:21.872
THEIR ACCOUNTS MATCH.

03:21.872 --> 03:25.165
MR. LeMARCHAL STEPPED BACKWARDS,
STUMBLED, AND FELL.

03:26.587 --> 03:29.129
SO YOU'RE RULING IT
AN ACCIDENT.

03:29.129 --> 03:31.962
UNLESS I LEARN SOMETHING
THAT SUGGESTS OTHERWISE.

03:31.962 --> 03:34.295
YOU KNOW, WE FOUND AN ODD THING
AT THE SCENE.

03:34.295 --> 03:36.176
IT WAS PRETTY CURIOUS,
ACTUALLY.

03:36.176 --> 03:38.469
DID YOU KNOW
YOUR DAD WAS WEARING A WIRE?

03:39.550 --> 03:40.721
NO.

03:40.721 --> 03:42.343
I CHECKED WITH
OTHER LAW-ENFORCEMENT AGENCIES

03:42.343 --> 03:43.974
TO SEE IF HE WAS WORKING
WITH ANY OF THEM.

03:43.974 --> 03:45.346
HE WASN'T.

03:45.346 --> 03:48.188
MY FATHER WAS KNOWN
TO TAPE BUSINESS CONVERSATIONS

03:48.188 --> 03:51.272
WITH THOSE
HE FOUND UNTRUSTWORTHY.

03:51.272 --> 03:54.315
HE DID NOT TRUST
CONRAD GRAYSON.

03:55.356 --> 03:57.488
THEN YOU THINK
WHAT I THINK --

03:57.488 --> 03:59.490
THERE'S MORE TO THIS
THAN WE KNOW.

04:02.122 --> 04:05.035
[ BOAT HORN BLOWS ]

04:05.035 --> 04:07.748
[ BEEP ]
 EMILY. HEY.
THIS IS MY THIRD MESSAGE.

04:07.748 --> 04:09.630
I NEED TO SHOW YOU SOMETHING.

04:09.630 --> 04:11.462
MIGHT BE NOTHING, BUT JUST --

04:11.462 --> 04:13.834
JUST IN CASE,
CALL ME WHEN YOU GET THIS.

04:13.834 --> 04:15.085
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

04:15.085 --> 04:16.216
JACK, RIGHT?

04:16.216 --> 04:19.470
JAVIER.
NOLAN'S FEDERAL PEN PAL.

04:19.470 --> 04:21.932
HAD ME HELP YOU OUT ON THE PHONE
A WHILE BACK.

04:21.932 --> 04:23.263
WELL, FROM WHAT I HEAR,

04:23.263 --> 04:25.596
YOUR FRIENDSHIP STATUS
IS DEBATABLE.

04:27.388 --> 04:29.890
ANYWAY, I'M, UH,
I'M LOOKING FOR CHARLOTTE.

04:29.890 --> 04:32.313
SHE HASN'T ANSWERED ANY CALLS
OR TEXTS SINCE LAST NIGHT,

04:32.313 --> 04:33.894
SO I TRACED
HER PHONE SIGNAL,

04:33.894 --> 04:35.946
AND THE LAST PING
OFF THE CELL TOWER

04:35.946 --> 04:37.898
ORIGINATED FROM HERE,
AROUND 10:00.

04:37.898 --> 04:41.111
THAT WAS WHEN HER PHONE DIED
AND SHE LEFT.

04:41.111 --> 04:42.533
DID SHE SAY ANYTHING --

04:42.533 --> 04:44.455
WHERE SHE WAS GOING,
PLANS FOR TODAY?

04:47.998 --> 04:50.170
I'M GONNA CHECK IN
WITH SOME PEOPLE.

04:50.170 --> 04:52.463
I'LL CALL YOU
IF I FIND OUT ANYTHING, OKAY?

04:52.463 --> 04:54.174
YEAH.

04:58.088 --> 04:59.259
THANKS.

04:59.259 --> 05:02.182
YEAH. THANK YOU.

05:02.182 --> 05:05.055
[ COMPUTER CHIMING ]

05:12.523 --> 05:15.195
[ WHIMPERS ]

05:16.316 --> 05:17.818
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

05:21.612 --> 05:22.823
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

05:22.823 --> 05:25.035
EMILY: [ Distorted ]
I have your daughter.

05:25.035 --> 05:26.577
[ Normal ] WOULD YOU LIKE
TO GET HER BACK?

05:26.577 --> 05:27.828
WHO IS THIS?

05:27.828 --> 05:30.371
[ Distorted ] Flight 197
destroyed many lives,

05:30.371 --> 05:32.583
SO I'M DESTROYING YOURS.

05:32.583 --> 05:34.755
TO ENSURE
CHARLOTTE'S SAFE RETURN,

05:34.755 --> 05:36.417
YOU AND HER MOTHER

05:36.417 --> 05:38.669
WILL CONFESS YOUR INVOLVEMENT
IN THAT TERRORIST ACT

05:38.669 --> 05:41.131
AND THE SUBSEQUENT FRAMING
OF AN INNOCENT MAN.

05:41.131 --> 05:43.964
[ Distorted ] Do not alert
the police or anyone else,

05:43.964 --> 05:45.345
or there will be
consequences.

05:46.387 --> 05:47.888
[ Dial tone ]

05:47.888 --> 05:49.730
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

05:49.730 --> 05:50.731
[ SIGHS ]

05:50.731 --> 05:52.022
[ DOOR OPENS ]

05:52.022 --> 05:54.184
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:54.184 --> 05:56.777
[ CHARLOTTE SOBBING ]

06:01.151 --> 06:03.243
THIS IS WORSE
THAN I THOUGHT.

06:03.243 --> 06:06.487
NICE JOB ON
THE VOICE-ALTERING PROGRAM.

06:06.487 --> 06:08.949
LOVE THE COMPLIMENT,

06:08.949 --> 06:10.991
BUT WHAT I NEED
IS REASSURANCE

06:10.991 --> 06:13.954
THAT WHAT WE ARE DOING
IS NOT COMPLETELY MESSED UP.

06:13.954 --> 06:16.256
WITH PASCAL DEAD,
CHARLOTTE'S ALL I HAVE LEFT.

06:16.256 --> 06:17.668
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

06:17.668 --> 06:18.919
SHE'S THE ONLY PERSON

06:18.919 --> 06:21.171
THAT VICTORIA AND CONRAD
WOULD DO ANYTHING FOR.

06:21.171 --> 06:23.053
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

06:23.053 --> 06:24.715
DON'T ANSWER!

06:24.715 --> 06:27.428
IT'S JACK. HE'S CALLED TWICE.
WHAT IF HE'S IN TROUBLE?

06:27.428 --> 06:29.430
NO CONTACT
WITH ANYBODY OUTSIDE THIS GROUP

06:29.430 --> 06:30.971
UNTIL THIS IS OVER.

06:30.971 --> 06:32.473
I COULDN'T GET HER
TO EAT ANYTHING.

06:32.473 --> 06:35.015
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
 AND ARE THE CUFFS
REALLY NECESSARY?

06:35.015 --> 06:36.226
YOU DON'T KIDNAP SOMEBODY
HALFWAY, NOLAN.

06:36.226 --> 06:38.108
I WOULD NEVER
HURT CHARLOTTE, NOLAN.

06:38.108 --> 06:39.940
IF YOU DON'T TRUST ME,
THERE'S THE DOOR.

06:41.692 --> 06:43.984
LOOK, I WANT YOU HERE,

06:43.984 --> 06:46.787
BUT IF YOU STAY,
THIS PLAN DOESN'T END

06:46.787 --> 06:49.950
UNTIL VICTORIA AND CONRAD
ARE BEHIND BARS TONIGHT.

06:51.241 --> 06:52.493
SO?

06:53.914 --> 06:56.376
SO...

06:56.376 --> 06:58.168
LET'S BAG SOME GRAYSONS.

07:18.519 --> 07:19.860
[ COMPUTER PINGS ]

07:19.860 --> 07:21.862
[ Ringing ]

07:21.862 --> 07:23.363
[ SIGHS ]

07:23.363 --> 07:26.156
AS PREDICTED,
CONRAD PLACED A CALL.

07:26.156 --> 07:29.870
[ Ringing continues ]

07:29.870 --> 07:33.033
DUKE MARINO --
ONE OF HIS THUGS-FOR-HIRE.

07:33.033 --> 07:35.165
I AM HIJACKING THE LINE,

07:35.165 --> 07:38.128
SENDING IT
TO A DUMMY VOICEMAIL.

07:38.128 --> 07:42.212
Man: YOU HAVE REACHED
 THE MAILBOX OF 555-0183.

07:42.212 --> 07:43.714
LEAVE A MESSAGE.
 [ BEEP ]

07:43.714 --> 07:47.007
MR. MARINO,
 THIS IS CONRAD GRAYSON.

07:47.007 --> 07:49.469
MEET ME AT WHARF 16
 IN AN HOUR.

07:49.469 --> 07:51.261
[ Dial tone ]

07:51.261 --> 07:52.513
[ CLICK ]

07:55.055 --> 07:57.808
RIGHT, THEN.
OFF TO THE MORGUE.

07:59.770 --> 08:01.271
Daniel:
YOU SHOULDN'T BE HERE.

08:02.773 --> 08:05.275
MY FATHER WOULD WANT ME
TO BE STRONG.

08:05.275 --> 08:08.238
I WROTE HIS OBITUARY
THIS MORNING.

08:08.238 --> 08:09.570
THE TIME WE SHARED HERE

08:09.570 --> 08:12.492
ALLOWED ME TO HONOR HIM
AS A DAUGHTER,

08:12.492 --> 08:15.245
NOT JUST HIS EMPLOYEE.

08:15.245 --> 08:18.919
OUR LAST EXCHANGE
WAS SUCH A GOOD ONE.

08:18.919 --> 08:21.041
HE TOLD ME HE --

08:21.041 --> 08:25.546
HE LOVED ME AND WAS PROUD
OF MY ACCOMPLISHMENTS.

08:25.546 --> 08:27.177
HEY.

08:27.177 --> 08:29.429
HEY, YOU'RE GONNA
GET THROUGH THIS, OKAY?

08:32.683 --> 08:35.846
WHAT ARE YOU WATCHING?

08:35.846 --> 08:38.227
UH, WELL,
THE DETECTIVE ON THE CASE

08:38.227 --> 08:43.023
ASKED FOR ALL SECURITY FOOTAGE
FROM LeMARCHAL HEADQUARTERS.

08:43.023 --> 08:45.906
I MADE A COPY FOR MYSELF.

08:45.906 --> 08:48.238
WHY --
WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT?

08:55.455 --> 08:58.118
YOU THINK
MY DAD KILLED PASCAL?

09:00.540 --> 09:02.002
YES.

09:12.052 --> 09:14.054
I THINK HE DID, TOO.

09:14.054 --> 09:15.305
IT'S NO SECRET

09:15.305 --> 09:17.347
MY DAD WAS GUNNING FOR HIM
ON THE BUSINESS SIDE,

09:17.347 --> 09:19.059
BUT AS SOON AS
PASCAL AND MY MOTHER

09:19.059 --> 09:21.391
REKINDLED THEIR RELATIONSHIP,
TENSIONS ESCALATED.

09:21.391 --> 09:24.184
TO THE POINT WHERE MY FATHER
WAS WEARING A WIRE

09:24.184 --> 09:25.816
THE NIGHT HE DIED.

09:25.816 --> 09:28.899
HE MUST HAVE WANTED
TO CAPTURE SOMETHING
INCRIMINATING ON CONRAD.

09:28.899 --> 09:30.741
AND CONRAD
MUST HAVE FOUND OUT.

09:30.741 --> 09:32.953
AND HOW IS THIS
FOR A COINCIDENCE?

09:32.953 --> 09:36.657
ANY CAMERA WITH A CLEAR VIEW
OF THE HELIPAD

09:36.657 --> 09:38.408
WAS OUT OF ORDER.

09:38.408 --> 09:39.960
BUT LOOK
WHAT I JUST DISCOVERED.

09:39.960 --> 09:41.501
[ KEY CLICKS ]

09:41.501 --> 09:43.003
HERE IS THE STAIRWELL
FROM THE ROOF

09:43.003 --> 09:44.965
SECONDS AFTER THE ACCIDENT.

09:44.965 --> 09:47.467
I DON'T RECOGNIZE HER.

09:47.467 --> 09:48.879
DO YOU?

09:51.261 --> 09:53.173
NOT AT ALL.

09:56.016 --> 09:58.889
[ BUOY BELL CLANGING,
GULLS CRYING ]

09:58.889 --> 10:01.722
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

10:17.157 --> 10:19.369
[ Voice breaking ] PLEASE --
 DON'T COME ANY CLOSER.

10:19.369 --> 10:20.871
[ SMACK ]
 AAH!

10:20.871 --> 10:22.502
Emily: [ Distorted ] CALL
 A TELEVISED PRESS CONFERENCE

10:22.502 --> 10:24.244
FOR 6:00 P.M. AT GRAYSON MANOR.

10:24.244 --> 10:26.246
DO THIS,
 AND CHARLOTTE GOES FREE.

10:26.246 --> 10:27.668
[ CHARLOTTE MOANS ]
 DISOBEY ME AGAIN...

10:27.668 --> 10:30.630
...AND MORE OF
 WHAT'S IN THE BOX WILL ARRIVE.

10:46.186 --> 10:48.648
Charlotte:
 WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

10:48.648 --> 10:51.271
PLEASE --
 DON'T COME ANY CLOSER!

10:51.271 --> 10:53.073
[ SMACK ]
 AAH!

10:53.073 --> 10:55.535
TALK ABOUT
A SOFTWARE SUCK-IT.

10:55.535 --> 10:58.949
I FIXED THE BUGS
IN JAVIER'S MYCLONE APP.

10:58.949 --> 11:00.781
[ CHARLOTTE PANTING ]

11:00.781 --> 11:03.543
THIS MAY AS WELL BE
CHARLOTTE GRAYSON IN THE FLESH.

11:03.543 --> 11:04.705
[ Screaming ] NO!
 THAT'S ENOUGH.

11:04.705 --> 11:06.626
[ CRYING ]

11:06.626 --> 11:07.417
[ CLICK ]

11:07.417 --> 11:09.049
EASY, JUDGE JUDY.

11:09.049 --> 11:11.461
YOU WERE THE ONE
THAT SENT CONRAD AN EAR.

11:11.461 --> 11:13.673
I MEAN, SERIOUSLY,
DO YOU AND AIDEN FLIP A COIN

11:13.673 --> 11:15.175
FOR WHO RUNS
THE CREEPIEST ERRAND?

11:20.100 --> 11:21.141
[ SIGHS ]

11:23.143 --> 11:25.185
WHAT'S THE FIRST THING
YOU THINK YOU'LL DO

11:25.185 --> 11:27.067
AS AMANDA CLARKE?

11:32.813 --> 11:34.404
[ SCOFFS ]

11:34.404 --> 11:36.947
I MEAN, YOU'VE BEEN RUNNING
THIS RACE SINCE YOU WERE A KID.

11:36.947 --> 11:39.409
YOU HAVEN'T EVEN FANTASIZED
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENS

11:39.409 --> 11:41.912
WHEN YOU CROSS
THE FINISH LINE?

11:41.912 --> 11:44.084
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

11:44.084 --> 11:46.166
YOU KNOW
WHAT ALWAYS STUCK WITH ME?

11:46.166 --> 11:49.920
THAT TIME THAT YOU IMPLIED
I WAS A ROBOT.

11:49.920 --> 11:51.331
EMS, WE WERE IN A FIGHT.
I DIDN'T --

11:51.331 --> 11:54.424
EMILY THORNE
IS A MACHINE.

11:54.424 --> 11:56.967
THAT'S WHY
I CREATED HER.

11:59.179 --> 12:01.641
I HAD TO FIND A WAY
NOT TO FEEL.

12:07.687 --> 12:09.109
THE TRUTH IS...

12:11.401 --> 12:14.775
...I HAVE NO IDEA
WHO AMANDA CLARKE IS ANYMORE.

12:16.907 --> 12:20.620
[ BABY CRYING ]

12:26.787 --> 12:29.790
DID YOU HURT YOURSELF,
LITTLE MOUSE?

12:29.790 --> 12:31.631
I'M THE NANNY.
IS HE OKAY?

12:31.631 --> 12:34.464
OH, IT'S JUST
A LITTLE SCRATCH.

12:34.464 --> 12:36.676
WE ALL HAVE TO TAKE
OUR BUMPS AND BRUISES,

12:36.676 --> 12:38.048
DON'T WE, LITTLE CARL?

12:38.048 --> 12:39.930
I WAS LOOKING FOR JACK.

12:39.930 --> 12:42.843
OH, HE'S AT WORK.
CAN I GIVE HIM A MESSAGE?

12:42.843 --> 12:45.185
YOU'RE VERY KIND.

12:45.185 --> 12:47.938
BUT I WAS HOPING
TO CATCH HIM IN PERSON.

12:52.312 --> 12:54.104
Nanny: [ Playfully ]
LOOK AT THIS!

12:54.104 --> 12:55.655
LOOK AT THIS!

12:57.027 --> 12:58.899
[ DOOR OPENS ]

13:01.241 --> 13:02.492
[ SCREAMS ]

13:04.574 --> 13:05.615
STOP!

13:05.615 --> 13:07.707
Reporter:
 246 PASSENGER FATALITIES

13:07.707 --> 13:09.409
IN THE BOMBING
 OF THE JUMBO JET.

13:09.409 --> 13:11.711
Emily: [ Distorted ]
 FOR TOO LONG,
 YOU'VE HEARD THE RUMORS

13:11.711 --> 13:12.873
OF CONRAD GRAYSON'S
 IMMORAL ACTS

13:12.873 --> 13:15.215
AND THEN BURIED YOUR HEAD
 IN THE SAND.

13:15.215 --> 13:18.008
TODAY, I'M SHOWING YOU
 THE TRUTH.

13:18.008 --> 13:20.420
WHAT?
 THE BOMBING OF FLIGHT 197
 DECIMATED MY FAMILY.

13:20.420 --> 13:23.223
DID YOU EVER WONDER ABOUT
 THE PEOPLE WHO DIED THAT DAY,

13:23.223 --> 13:25.225
SLAUGHTERED BY CONRAD GRAYSON?

13:25.225 --> 13:28.929
HE'S A BUSINESSMAN!
HE DIDN'T PUT A BOMB ON A PLANE!

13:28.929 --> 13:30.600
HE LAUNDERED MONEY
 FOR THE TERRORISTS WHO DID.

13:30.600 --> 13:32.022
HE'S JUST AS GUILTY.

13:32.022 --> 13:34.104
Reporter:
 FOR THE DOWNING OF FLIGHT 197,

13:34.104 --> 13:38.778
ALL 246 AMERICANS ON BOARD
 THAT FLIGHT WERE KILLED.

13:38.778 --> 13:41.201
Woman:
 KELLY AND PATRICK SIMMONS.

13:41.201 --> 13:42.782
Man: UZARSKI FAMILY.

13:42.782 --> 13:43.864
Woman: ERIN MAYO.

13:43.864 --> 13:45.615
BRETT AND ELIZABETH RICHARDS.

13:45.615 --> 13:46.997
[ REPORTERS SHOUTING QUESTIONS ]

13:46.997 --> 13:50.500
Emily: [ Distorted ]
 I DON'T WANT TO TORTURE YOU.

13:50.500 --> 13:52.832
I WANT TO TEACH YOU.

13:52.832 --> 13:54.875
[ CHARLOTTE CRYING ]

13:57.087 --> 14:01.091
[ Normal ] CHARLOTTE, PLEASE --
OPEN YOUR EYES.

14:01.091 --> 14:03.723
Man: RICHARD LUCAS.

14:06.016 --> 14:08.728
DEREK WILSON.

14:08.728 --> 14:10.810
Emily: [ Distorted ]
 WHEN EXPOSURE THREATENED

14:10.810 --> 14:12.062
[ Normal ]
YOUR FAMILY'S LIFE OF PRIVILEGE,

14:12.062 --> 14:14.774
CONRAD TURNED TO YOUR MOTHER
TO COVER HIS TRACKS.

14:14.774 --> 14:16.526
SHE CHOSE DAVID CLARKE,

14:16.526 --> 14:18.148
[ Distorted ] YOUR FATHER,

14:18.148 --> 14:19.980
TO TAKE THE FALL.

14:19.980 --> 14:21.361
Reporter: MOMENTS AGO,

14:21.361 --> 14:22.943
A JURY FOUND TERRORIST
 CONSPIRATOR DAVID CLARKE

14:22.943 --> 14:24.694
GUILTY ON ALL COUNTS.

14:24.694 --> 14:26.156
Emily: [ Distorted ] BUT HOW
 MANY PEOPLE WOULD BE NEEDED

14:26.156 --> 14:27.537
TO PULL OFF SUCH A CONSPIRACY?

14:27.537 --> 14:28.868
NO!

14:28.868 --> 14:31.291
HOW FAR WOULD THEY GO
TO FRAME AN INNOCENT MAN?

14:31.291 --> 14:33.914
Reporter:
 FEDERAL PROSECUTORS WRAPPED UP
 THEIR CASE FOR TREASON

14:33.914 --> 14:36.997
AGAINST DISGRACED HEDGE-FUND
 EXECUTIVE DAVID CLARKE.

14:36.997 --> 14:39.089
GRAYSON PUT YOU
 UP TO THIS, DIDN'T HE?!

14:39.089 --> 14:42.802
GRAYSON'S TESTIMONY
DETAILED THE SCHEME CLARKE USED

14:42.802 --> 14:44.054
[ Sobbing ] OH, GOD!
 TO CHANNEL MONEY
 TO THE TERRORISTS

14:44.054 --> 14:47.347
RESPONSIBLE FOR THE DOWNING
 OF FLIGHT 197.

14:47.347 --> 14:49.970
David: I HAVE A FAMILY,

14:49.970 --> 14:53.063
[ GAVEL POUNDING ]
 AND YOU'RE SENDING ME TO PRISON
 FOR A CRIME I DIDN'T DO!

14:53.063 --> 14:54.144
AND YOU KNOW IT!

14:54.144 --> 14:56.106
[ Sobbing ] NO MORE!

14:56.106 --> 14:57.727
WHO ELSE WOULD THEY ELIMINATE
TO PROTECT THEIR PLOT?

14:58.728 --> 15:00.280
Charlotte: PLEASE STOP!

15:02.022 --> 15:04.945
Javier: HEY.

15:04.945 --> 15:05.905
CHECK OUT THAT SUNSET.

15:05.905 --> 15:07.988
[ Sobbing ] NO!

15:10.530 --> 15:12.412
TURN IT OFF!

15:12.412 --> 15:14.995
YOUR PARENTS' CRIMES
CAN'T GO UNCHECKED ANY LONGER.

15:14.995 --> 15:17.587
DO YOU HAVE THE STRENGTH
TO CALL THEM OUT?
 [ DOOR OPENS ]

15:17.587 --> 15:19.039
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

15:19.039 --> 15:22.002
[ CHARLOTTE SOBBING ]

15:39.559 --> 15:40.940
Conrad: VICTORIA.

15:44.654 --> 15:46.486
[ SOBBING ]

15:47.617 --> 15:48.738
MURDERER!

15:48.738 --> 15:50.991
HOW DARE YOU
SHOW YOUR FACE HERE!

15:50.991 --> 15:52.162
IF YOU'D ANSWERED
MY CALLS,

15:52.162 --> 15:54.034
YOU'D KNOW
CHARLOTTE'S BEEN ABDUCTED!

15:54.034 --> 15:56.916
THEY TOOK HER
AND SENT ME THIS!

15:56.916 --> 15:58.168
OHH!

15:58.168 --> 15:59.499
NOW WILL YOU LISTEN?

15:59.499 --> 16:02.582
A MAN CONTACTED ME
THIS MORNING.

16:02.582 --> 16:05.845
THE BOMBING OF 197
HAS DESTROYED HIS LIFE.

16:05.845 --> 16:08.088
HE BLAMES US
AND DEMANDS

16:08.088 --> 16:10.220
THAT WE TELL THE WORLD
WHAT WE'VE DONE.

16:11.971 --> 16:15.305
OH, MY GOD. THIS IS --
THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING.

16:15.305 --> 16:16.856
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

16:16.856 --> 16:18.858
I'M CALLING
THE AUTHORITIES.

16:18.858 --> 16:20.270
NO, I ALREADY TESTED
THE BOUNDARIES.

16:20.270 --> 16:22.942
THIS...
WAS THE CONSEQUENCE.

16:22.942 --> 16:25.735
WE'LL DO
AS HE INSTRUCTED --

16:25.735 --> 16:27.947
CALL A PRESS CONFERENCE
AND COME CLEAN.

16:29.869 --> 16:31.821
CHARLOTTE...

16:31.821 --> 16:33.873
SHOULDN'T PERISH
FOR OUR SINS.

16:33.873 --> 16:35.535
OUR SINS?

16:35.535 --> 16:38.078
I WILL DO
WHATEVER THIS ABDUCTOR WANTS,

16:38.078 --> 16:39.789
BUT BE CLEAR --

16:39.789 --> 16:42.212
WHAT'S HAPPENING
IS A RESULT

16:42.212 --> 16:45.085
OF YOUR DEPLORABLE,
GREEDY ACTIONS 20 YEARS AGO.

16:45.085 --> 16:48.888
IF CHARLOTTE DIES,
THIS WILL BE YOUR FAULT.

16:48.888 --> 16:51.931
IF YOU NEED TO LAY BLAME,
THEN KEEP IN MIND

16:51.931 --> 16:54.974
THAT IT WAS YOUR ROMANTIC
ENTANGLEMENT WITH DAVID

16:54.974 --> 16:58.398
THAT BROUGHT HER INTO THIS WORLD
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

16:58.398 --> 17:00.810
I SHOWED HER LOVE
WHEN I DIDN'T HAVE TO.

17:00.810 --> 17:02.902
AND THOUGH
SHE WAS BORN OF BETRAYAL,

17:02.902 --> 17:08.358
I WILL NOT
 LET HER DIE THAT WAY.

17:08.358 --> 17:10.859
YOU ABDUCTED CHARLOTTE
TO GET THE GRAYSONS TO CONFESS?

17:10.859 --> 17:12.321
HOW DID YOU EVEN FIND US?
 CHARLOTTE WAS MISSING.

17:12.321 --> 17:14.074
I THOUGHT
 THAT I NEEDED YOUR HELP.

17:14.074 --> 17:15.704
BUT THEN WHEN YOU GUYS
DIDN'T ANSWER MY CALLS,
I KNEW SOMETHING WAS UP,

17:15.704 --> 17:17.827
SO I HAD HER BOYFRIEND
TRACK NOLAN'S PHONE.

17:17.827 --> 17:19.618
JAVIER KNOWS
WHERE WE ARE?
 SO WHAT?!

17:19.618 --> 17:20.960
NO ONE
IN THEIR RIGHT MIND

17:20.960 --> 17:22.252
WOULD THINK YOU GUYS ARE
UP TO SOMETHING THIS SICK.

17:22.252 --> 17:23.873
YOU NEED TO LEAVE.
 WHY?

17:23.873 --> 17:25.755
SO YOU DON'T HAVE TO
CONFRONT YOUR CONSCIENCE?

17:25.755 --> 17:29.509
OKAY, I'M GONNA TAKE CARE
OF THAT...THING FROM HOME.

17:29.509 --> 17:31.381
JACK,
I AM SO CLOSE TO THE END.

17:31.381 --> 17:33.433
BY TONIGHT, VICTORIA AND CONRAD
WILL BE FINISHED.

17:33.433 --> 17:34.844
OUR FATHER'S NAME
WILL BE CLEARED.

17:34.844 --> 17:35.935
WHAT ABOUT CHARLOTTE?

17:35.935 --> 17:37.937
SHE CAN FINALLY
LIVE IN TRUTH.

17:37.937 --> 17:39.939
YOU WILL NEVER HAVE
A RELATIONSHIP WITH
YOUR SISTER AFTER THIS.

17:39.939 --> 17:41.060
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

17:41.060 --> 17:42.562
I NEED EMILY.

17:42.562 --> 17:44.023
JUST EMILY.

17:45.105 --> 17:46.816
WHAT?

17:46.816 --> 17:48.358
SHE'S HAVING
A PANIC ATTACK.

17:48.358 --> 17:50.150
WELL, IT'LL PASS. I HAD THEM
ALL THE TIME WHEN I WAS A KID.

17:50.150 --> 17:51.401
JUST SLOW THINGS DOWN.

17:51.401 --> 17:52.822
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

17:52.822 --> 17:54.654
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO SAID
THAT WE CAN'T DO THINGS HALFWAY.

17:54.654 --> 17:57.697
ALL I CAN SEE OUT THERE
IS COLLEEN.

17:57.697 --> 17:59.078
[ SIGHS ]

17:59.078 --> 18:01.121
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR SISTER
WAS TOTALLY DIFFERENT.

18:01.121 --> 18:02.792
SHE WAS KIDNAPPED
AND USED AS LEVERAGE

18:02.792 --> 18:04.754
TO FORCE MY FATHER TO DO
SOMETHING AGAINST HIS WILL.

18:04.754 --> 18:06.296
SHE WAS TERRORIZED,
TORTURED, AND KILLED.

18:06.296 --> 18:08.418
THAT IS NOT GONNA HAPPEN
TO CHARLOTTE. YOU KNOW THAT.

18:08.418 --> 18:10.470
SHE DOESN'T.

18:10.470 --> 18:12.842
WE CAN'T ALLOW HER
TO SUFFER.

18:14.424 --> 18:15.425
[ SIGHS ]

18:15.425 --> 18:16.676
FINE.
I'LL GO TO THE PHARMACY.

18:16.676 --> 18:17.927
I'LL GET SOMETHING
TO CALM HER DOWN.

18:17.927 --> 18:19.349
TAKE PORTER WITH YOU.

18:19.349 --> 18:20.680
YOU KICK ME OUT,

18:20.680 --> 18:21.851
AND I WILL BLOW THE WHISTLE
ON THIS WHOLE THING.

18:21.851 --> 18:23.353
I'M NOT LEAVING CHARLOTTE.

18:23.353 --> 18:24.684
WOW.

18:24.684 --> 18:26.356
WHERE WERE YOU TWO HEROES
WHEN I WAS 9 YEARS OLD,

18:26.356 --> 18:28.528
BEING DRAGGED OUT OF MY HOUSE
BY MEN WITH GUNS,

18:28.528 --> 18:30.109
THROWN INTO
THE FOSTER-CARE SYSTEM?

18:30.109 --> 18:31.821
CHARLOTTE HAS
ALWAYS BEEN PROTECTED,

18:31.821 --> 18:34.194
AND SHE WILL BE FINE NOW.

18:36.496 --> 18:37.827
[ DOOR OPENS ]

18:44.914 --> 18:47.086
TAKE CHARLOTTE'S HAIR
AND CARL'S BLOOD TO THE LAB,

18:47.086 --> 18:50.340
AND TELL THEM
IT REQUIRES IMMEDIATE ATTENTION.

18:50.340 --> 18:51.551
AND IF THEY'RE BUSY?

18:51.551 --> 18:54.093
I'LL PAY WHATEVER IT TAKES.
HURRY, PLEASE.

18:54.093 --> 18:55.635
A LIFE DEPENDS ON IT.

19:01.851 --> 19:03.433
EMILY THORNE?

19:04.764 --> 19:05.855
YES?

19:05.855 --> 19:08.688
I'M DETECTIVE HOSKO,
NYPD.

19:08.688 --> 19:12.111
WE'RE LOOKING INTO THE DEATH
OF PASCAL LeMARCHAL.

19:12.111 --> 19:15.074
I THINK YOU MAY HAVE SOME
INFORMATION THAT COULD HELP US.

19:15.074 --> 19:17.947
ACTUALLY, I DIDN'T KNOW
MR. LeMARCHAL VERY WELL AT ALL.

19:17.947 --> 19:19.829
HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW
CONRAD GRAYSON?

19:21.451 --> 19:23.743
HE'S MY EX-FATHER-IN-LAW.

19:23.743 --> 19:28.628
I HEARD HE WAS ON THE ROOF
WHEN MR. LeMARCHAL DIED.

19:29.959 --> 19:31.791
DO YOU SUSPECT FOUL PLAY?

19:33.092 --> 19:35.425
IS CONRAD IN CUSTODY?

19:35.425 --> 19:37.297
WE'LL HASH THAT OUT
AT THE STATION.

19:37.297 --> 19:39.799
ACTUALLY, IT'S REALLY NOT
A GOOD TIME FOR ME RIGHT NOW.

19:39.799 --> 19:41.851
I'M AFRAID YOU DON'T HAVE
MUCH OF A CHOICE.

19:43.473 --> 19:45.725
WELL, THEN...
I'LL MEET YOU IN THE CITY.

19:45.725 --> 19:48.147
YOU KNOW WHAT?
THERE WAS A PILEUP ON THE L.I.E.

19:48.147 --> 19:50.690
TRAFFIC'S BACKED UP
FOR MILES.

19:50.690 --> 19:51.811
RIDE WITH ME.

19:51.811 --> 19:54.023
I'LL LIGHT IT UP,
GET US THERE IN NO TIME.

20:11.501 --> 20:13.002
SECURITY CAMERAS
CAPTURED THIS.

20:13.002 --> 20:14.714
PER THE TIME STAMP, THIS PERSON
WITNESSED MR. LeMARCHAL

20:14.714 --> 20:17.337
GETTING ACQUAINTED
WITH THAT HELICOPTER BLADE.

20:17.337 --> 20:18.678
SOMEONE SAYS IT'S YOU.

20:18.678 --> 20:20.600
[ LAUGHS ]
WELL, IT ISN'T.

20:20.600 --> 20:22.181
YOU WERE THERE, THOUGH.

20:22.181 --> 20:23.513
WELL,
IN THE BUILDING, YES.

20:23.513 --> 20:25.685
THE PHOTOGRAPHER HIRED
TO DOCUMENT THAT PARTY

20:25.685 --> 20:27.347
DOESN'T HAVE
A SINGLE SHOT OF YOU.

20:27.347 --> 20:28.518
WHY WOULD THAT BE?

20:28.518 --> 20:31.351
WHAT -- YOU THINK
I'M INVOLVED IN THIS?

20:31.351 --> 20:32.692
MIND ANSWERING
THE QUESTION?

20:33.773 --> 20:36.115
HE WAS PROBABLY INSTRUCTED
NOT TO TAKE MY PICTURE.

20:36.115 --> 20:37.947
THE GRAYSONS DESPISE ME.

20:37.947 --> 20:40.620
REALLY? I HEARD
YOU AND MR. GRAYSON WERE TIGHT.

20:40.620 --> 20:42.912
YOU TWO EVER DISCUSS THE AX
HE HAD TO GRIND WITH PASCAL?

20:43.863 --> 20:47.667
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

20:47.667 --> 20:49.539
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

20:49.539 --> 20:50.830
EMS. HEY.

20:50.830 --> 20:52.081
Detective Hosko...

20:52.081 --> 20:54.874
I haven't talked to Conrad
in weeks.
 EMS?

20:54.874 --> 20:58.588
I'M SORRY
I'M...NOT MORE HELP.

20:58.588 --> 20:59.759
HOSKO:
That's nice of you.

20:59.759 --> 21:01.721
I'll admit the longer
I look at this case,

21:01.721 --> 21:03.513
the more questions I have.

21:03.513 --> 21:06.596
For example, why was
Mr. LeMarchal wearing
a wire when he died?

21:06.596 --> 21:09.729
AND WHOSE PARTIAL PRINT
DID WE FIND ON IT?

21:10.650 --> 21:11.981
That person's
got to know something.

21:11.981 --> 21:13.733
I WOULD IMAGINE SO.

21:13.733 --> 21:15.485
WE'RE ASKING THOSE
ASSOCIATED WITH PASCAL

21:15.485 --> 21:17.357
to, uh, volunteer
elimination prints.

21:17.357 --> 21:18.358
LOOK, I KNOW MY RIGHTS.

21:18.358 --> 21:19.609
IF YOU WANT THEM,

21:19.609 --> 21:21.321
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO CHARGE ME
WITH SOMETHING.

21:21.321 --> 21:23.573
Daniel:
YOU WANT A COPY OF HER PRINTS,
JUST PULL HER JUVIE FILE.

21:23.573 --> 21:26.165
MY EX-WIFE IS
A FORMER DELINQUENT, AFTER ALL.

21:27.957 --> 21:29.749
HANG TIGHT, MS. THORNE.

21:31.080 --> 21:33.292
WHAT DID YOU SAY TO HIM?

21:33.292 --> 21:35.174
JUST THAT I KNEW
MY FORMER BRIDE'S BODY

21:35.174 --> 21:36.506
WHEN I SAW IT.

21:36.506 --> 21:39.589
THAT'S YOU
IN THAT STAIRWELL.

21:39.589 --> 21:41.050
NO DOUBT.

21:41.050 --> 21:42.972
POOR DANIEL.

21:42.972 --> 21:44.974
SO BITTER
ABOUT OUR DIVORCE.

21:44.974 --> 21:47.387
ALWAYS TRYING
TO STIR UP TROUBLE FOR ME.

21:47.387 --> 21:49.689
YOU GOT IT, BABE.

21:49.689 --> 21:51.481
THE POLICE HAVE EMILY.

21:51.481 --> 21:52.772
HAS SHE BEEN ARRESTED?

21:52.772 --> 21:54.694
No, but they're questioning her
about Pascal.

21:54.694 --> 21:56.145
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:56.145 --> 21:59.068
SHE SLY-DIALED OUT ON HER PHONE
SO I COULD LISTEN IN.

21:59.068 --> 22:00.900
THEY'VE GOT
THE WIRE WE USED,

22:00.900 --> 22:03.533
AND THERE'S A PARTIAL PRINT
ON IT.

22:03.533 --> 22:05.995
CAN'T BE ONE OF OURS.
I WIPED THE DEVICE DOWN
BEFORE I PUT IT ON HIM.

22:05.995 --> 22:09.328
Let's err on the side
of caution, why don't we?

22:09.328 --> 22:10.870
ESPECIALLY SINCE
THEY'RE RUNNING THE PRINT

22:10.870 --> 22:12.121
AGAINST
EMILY'S JUVIE RECORD.

22:12.121 --> 22:14.123
She switched those records
with Amanda

22:14.123 --> 22:16.255
when they swapped
identities.

22:16.255 --> 22:18.418
IF EMILY'S PRINT
HAPPENS TO BE ON THAT WIRE,

22:18.418 --> 22:20.670
THEY'RE GONNA COME BACK
BELONGING TO A DEAD WOMAN.

22:20.670 --> 22:23.673
I AM CYBER-STALLING
THE COPS' SEARCH

22:23.673 --> 22:25.555
WHILE I HACK
THE NATIONAL DATABASE.

22:25.555 --> 22:29.889
THERE'S, UM...
JUST ONE PROBLEM I CAN'T FIX.

22:29.889 --> 22:31.521
DANIEL'S AT THE STATION.

22:31.521 --> 22:34.023
HE GOT
THIS WHOLE BALL ROLLING.

22:34.023 --> 22:35.645
I'll get down there.

22:35.645 --> 22:37.397
[ SIGHS ]

22:37.397 --> 22:39.068
EMILY'S BEEN SIDELINED.

22:39.068 --> 22:41.110
I'M GOING TO MANHATTAN.
YOU WATCH CHARLOTTE.

22:41.110 --> 22:43.242
I'M NOT HELPING YOU.

22:49.579 --> 22:52.331
WHY ARE YOU HERE, JACK?

22:52.331 --> 22:55.545
'CAUSE I CARE ABOUT THE INNOCENT
PERSON LOCKED UP IN THERE.

22:55.545 --> 22:57.797
YOU'RE NOT JUST HERE
FOR CHARLOTTE.

22:57.797 --> 22:59.549
YOU'RE WORRIED
ABOUT EMILY.

22:59.549 --> 23:03.002
FOR HER SOUL...
 MAYBE.

23:06.806 --> 23:09.719
YOU KNOW, YOU --
YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT, UM...

23:09.719 --> 23:13.473
DESPITE MINE AND EMILY'S
NUMEROUS ATTEMPTS

23:13.473 --> 23:17.186
AT MAKING IT WORK,
IT -- IT...

23:17.186 --> 23:18.688
IT HASN'T.

23:23.322 --> 23:24.824
I HAVE TO LET HER GO.

23:24.824 --> 23:27.527
BUT YOU --
 YOU OBVIOUSLY CAN'T.

23:27.527 --> 23:30.700
THAT'S WHY YOU HAVEN'T
RUNG THE AUTHORITIES ALREADY.

23:32.832 --> 23:34.534
YOU STILL CARE ABOUT HER.

23:36.245 --> 23:38.998
BUT THE PROBLEM IS,
YOU DON'T WANT HER.

23:38.998 --> 23:40.630
YOU WANT AMANDA CLARKE,

23:40.630 --> 23:43.092
THAT GIRL YOU CHERISHED
SO LONG AGO.

23:43.092 --> 23:45.004
NOW, YOU WILL
 SEE THAT GIRL AGAIN,

23:45.004 --> 23:48.758
BUT ONLY
IF THIS PLAN SUCCEEDS.

23:51.430 --> 23:54.053
LATE-BREAKING NEWS --
 CONRAD AND VICTORIA GRAYSON

23:54.053 --> 23:56.726
WILL MAKE A MAJOR ANNOUNCEMENT
 IN JUST A FEW HOURS.

23:56.726 --> 23:58.608
WE'LL BE LIVE WITH THE DETAILS.

23:58.608 --> 24:00.019
[ REMOTE CLICKS ]

24:00.019 --> 24:01.521
MONEY TALKS.

24:04.614 --> 24:06.526
[ DOOR OPENS ]

24:09.068 --> 24:10.490
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

24:13.623 --> 24:15.955
I'VE COMPOSED
OUR STATEMENTS.

24:15.955 --> 24:18.878
SAY WHAT YOU WANT.
I WON'T BE THERE.

24:18.878 --> 24:21.751
HE CLEARLY STIPULATED
WE BOTH SPEAK TONIGHT.

24:21.751 --> 24:23.462
I'VE CHANGED MY MIND.

24:23.462 --> 24:26.586
ABOUT WHAT --
SAVING YOUR DAUGHTER'S LIFE?

24:26.586 --> 24:29.549
IF CHARLOTTE WAS
EVER IN DANGER AT ALL.

24:29.549 --> 24:31.721
I THINK YOU CONCOCTED
THIS ENTIRE SCENARIO

24:31.721 --> 24:33.893
TO TRICK ME
INTO INCRIMINATING MYSELF.

24:33.893 --> 24:36.896
WOULD YOU PUT
YOUR CONTEMPT ASIDE

24:36.896 --> 24:38.477
AND PAY ATTENTION?

24:38.477 --> 24:40.600
I HAVE CRAFTED SOMETHING

24:40.600 --> 24:42.982
THAT PROTECTS
BOTH US AND CHARLOTTE.

24:42.982 --> 24:45.605
THE CONFESSIONS MADE
DURING THIS DOG-AND-PONY SHOW

24:45.605 --> 24:47.527
WILL BE CONSIDERED
UNDER DURESS

24:47.527 --> 24:49.318
AND INADMISSIBLE
IN A COURT OF LAW.

24:49.318 --> 24:52.702
THE KIDNAPPER'S A FOOL
NOT TO HAVE REALIZED THAT.

24:53.783 --> 24:55.615
AND YOU ARE A FOOL
TO THINK

24:55.615 --> 24:59.118
I'D EVER TRUST ANOTHER WORD
OUT OF YOUR VILE MOUTH.

25:06.546 --> 25:08.968
[ SIGHS ]

25:08.968 --> 25:10.219
OH, COME ON.

25:10.219 --> 25:12.131
Charlotte: HELLO?!

25:12.131 --> 25:15.304
YOU SENT ME THOSE LETTERS
PRETENDING TO BE DAVID CLARKE,

25:15.304 --> 25:17.306
DIDN'T YOU?

25:17.306 --> 25:19.398
I DON'T WANT
TO GET YOU IN TROUBLE.

25:19.398 --> 25:21.270
I JUST WANT TO TALK.

25:22.692 --> 25:24.644
YOU CAN TRUST ME.

25:28.027 --> 25:30.489
PLEASE -- TALK TO ME.

25:35.494 --> 25:37.206
[ SOBS, SNIFFLES ]

25:41.210 --> 25:43.002
PUT ON THE BLINDFOLD --

25:43.002 --> 25:44.584
[ Distorted ] NOW.

25:51.631 --> 25:53.432
[ DOOR OPENS ]

25:53.432 --> 25:55.264
[ SOBS LIGHTLY ]

25:55.264 --> 25:56.475
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

25:56.475 --> 25:57.727
DID I UPSET YOU?

25:57.727 --> 25:59.178
I DIDN'T MEAN TO.

26:00.730 --> 26:03.562
PLEASE, JUST TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON!

26:03.562 --> 26:05.144
[ HANDCUFFS RATTLE ]

26:07.607 --> 26:09.068
I'M LETTING YOU GO.

26:15.905 --> 26:17.576
I'M AT THE STATION.
HOW IS IT ON YOUR END?

26:17.576 --> 26:19.158
I AM ALTERING
EMILY AND AMANDA'S FINGERPRINTS

26:19.158 --> 26:22.581
SO THEY LEAD TO...
 TWO DEAD-END TRAILS.

26:22.581 --> 26:23.703
BRILLIANT.

26:23.703 --> 26:25.044
Look, I can't hold off
this detective's

26:25.044 --> 26:26.205
DATABASE SEARCH
MUCH LONGER.

26:26.205 --> 26:27.466
CAN YOU KEEP HIM OCCUPIED

26:27.466 --> 26:29.629
FOR -- I DON'T KNOW --
ANOTHER FIVE MINUTES?

26:29.629 --> 26:30.630
GLADLY.

26:30.630 --> 26:31.671
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

26:33.342 --> 26:36.015
Daniel:
I CAN'T WAIT FOR THOSE PRINTS
TO COME BACK AS YOURS.

26:36.015 --> 26:38.057
IT'LL SUPPORT A LITTLE THEORY
I HAVE GOING

26:38.057 --> 26:41.560
THAT YOU WERE PART
OF A CONSPIRACY TO KILL PASCAL.

26:41.560 --> 26:43.142
THE COPS
ARE GONNA LOVE IT.

26:43.142 --> 26:44.934
YOU SOUND
JUST LIKE YOUR MOTHER --

26:44.934 --> 26:46.485
COMPLETELY INSANE.

26:46.485 --> 26:49.649
DID YOU KNOW IMPERSONATING A
FEDERAL AGENT CARRIES A PENALTY?

26:49.649 --> 26:50.820
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

26:54.613 --> 26:56.035
COME ON! LET'S GO!
COME ON! GET OFF HIM!

26:56.035 --> 26:57.286
YOU SAW IT!

26:57.286 --> 27:00.289
THAT MAN ATTACKED ME
COMPLETELY UNPROVOKED!

27:00.289 --> 27:02.201
ARE YOU CRYING, DANIEL?
 NO.

27:02.201 --> 27:03.002
[ GRUNTS ]

27:03.002 --> 27:04.704
I'M PRESSING CHARGES.

27:04.704 --> 27:06.585
Officer: EASY. EASY.

27:06.585 --> 27:08.457
CALM DOWN, ALL RIGHT?

27:08.457 --> 27:10.840
ALL RIGHT. THANKS.

27:14.754 --> 27:16.465
Margaux: DANIEL?

27:19.929 --> 27:22.682
I SPOKE TO DETECTIVE HOSKO,
WHO TOLD ME YOU WERE HERE.

27:22.682 --> 27:24.934
HOW DARE YOU TAKE
SUSPICIONS ABOUT EMILY TO HIM

27:24.934 --> 27:26.225
WITHOUT TELLING ME.

27:26.225 --> 27:27.476
YOU USED
THIS INVESTIGATION

27:27.476 --> 27:29.689
TO FURTHER A VENDETTA
AGAINST YOUR EX-WIFE.

27:29.689 --> 27:32.651
NO, NOT A VENDETTA --
A HUNCH.

27:32.651 --> 27:33.983
HEY.

27:35.534 --> 27:37.656
I THINK EMILY WAS
WORKING WITH MY DAD.

27:37.656 --> 27:38.868
NOW, SHE MAY HAVE POSED

27:38.868 --> 27:40.870
AS A DEPARTMENT
OF HOMELAND SECURITY AGENT

27:40.870 --> 27:45.544
TO GET THAT WIRE ON PASCAL
AND PASCAL UP TO THAT ROOF.

27:45.544 --> 27:47.707
AND WHY WOULD CONRAD
HAVE EMILY DO THIS?

27:47.707 --> 27:50.459
I DON'T KNOW. THAT'S
WHY I WANTED HOSKO
TO TAKE A RUN AT HER.

27:50.459 --> 27:52.631
FAKE AGENTS,
RECORDING DEVICES --

27:52.631 --> 27:55.214
THIS GOES FAR BEYOND
BUSINESS RIVALRIES

27:55.214 --> 27:57.296
OR JEALOUSY
OVER VICTORIA.

27:57.296 --> 27:59.929
I DIDN'T WANT YOU
EXPOSED TO THIS.

27:59.929 --> 28:02.852
I NEED ANSWERS,
NOT PROTECTION.

28:04.353 --> 28:07.476
EVEN IF IT THREATENS
THE LAST MEMORY OF YOUR FATHER?

28:18.577 --> 28:19.909
YOUR PRINTS...

28:22.371 --> 28:23.622
...WERE NOT A MATCH.

28:25.244 --> 28:26.455
I'M NOT SURPRISED.

28:26.455 --> 28:27.666
HOW ABOUT A RIDE HOME?

28:27.666 --> 28:29.588
I'LL CALL A CAR.

28:29.588 --> 28:33.092
EMILY, THAT EX-HUSBAND OF YOURS
HAS IT OUT FOR YOU.

28:33.092 --> 28:34.713
THANKS FOR THE WARNING.

28:34.713 --> 28:36.756
I WASN'T GIVING YOU ONE.

28:36.756 --> 28:38.507
I GOT DECENT INSTINCTS
ABOUT PEOPLE.

28:38.507 --> 28:39.799
AFTER WATCHING YOU TODAY,

28:39.799 --> 28:41.600
I'M CERTAIN
THERE'S SOMEONE DANGEROUS

28:41.600 --> 28:43.973
HIDING IN THAT PRETTY,
LITTLE SOCIALITE SHELL.

28:45.434 --> 28:48.727
IT'S DANIEL GRAYSON
WHO SHOULD BE WORRIED.

28:48.727 --> 28:50.559
I'LL SEE YOU AROUND.

28:55.905 --> 28:57.817
Margaux:
EVEN AS A LITTLE GIRL,

28:57.817 --> 29:01.490
I PREFERRED
TO CALL MY FATHER "PASCAL."

29:01.490 --> 29:05.574
HE WAS SO DISTANT TO ME,
IT SEEMED RIGHT.

29:05.574 --> 29:09.628
BUT NOW I WONDER IF I WAS
KEEPING MY DISTANCE FROM HIM.

29:09.628 --> 29:13.582
PERHAPS I ALREADY SENSED
HE WAS EVIL TO HIS CORE.

29:16.755 --> 29:18.717
[ SNIFFLES ]

29:18.717 --> 29:20.759
[ Voice breaking ]
HOW DOES ONE GO ON WITH LIFE

29:20.759 --> 29:23.472
KNOWING THEY'VE DESCENDED
FROM SO MUCH HORROR?

29:23.472 --> 29:26.645
BY ABANDONING YOUR SOUL.

29:28.517 --> 29:30.269
IS THAT WHAT YOU'VE DONE?

29:31.480 --> 29:33.893
OH, DON'T DO
WHAT I'VE DONE.

29:33.893 --> 29:35.734
WELL, MAYBE I SHOULD.

29:35.734 --> 29:37.026
[ SNIFFLES ]

29:37.026 --> 29:39.358
IF IT MAKES DEALING
WITH THESE TRUTHS EASIER.

29:39.358 --> 29:40.399
PLEASE DON'T.

29:40.399 --> 29:42.571
WHY?

29:42.571 --> 29:46.785
BECAUSE SOMEDAY
I MAY NEED YOU TO SAVE ME.

29:55.624 --> 29:58.087
[ WHIMPERING ]

30:01.590 --> 30:02.631
[ WHIMPERS ]
 [ KNIFE CLICKS ]

30:02.631 --> 30:04.974
[ CRYING ]

30:09.348 --> 30:11.390
[ CRYING FADES, STOPS ]

30:21.740 --> 30:23.572
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

30:28.037 --> 30:30.449
THE PRESS CONFERENCE
IS MINUTES AWAY.

30:30.449 --> 30:32.041
NO WORD
 ON WHAT THE FORMER GOVERNOR

30:32.041 --> 30:33.622
AND HIS EX-WIFE PLAN TO SHARE,

30:33.622 --> 30:37.456
BUT WHEN THE GRAYSONS SPEAK,
 THE NEWS IS OFTEN EXPLOSIVE.

30:37.456 --> 30:39.338
[ REMOTE CLICKS ]

30:48.387 --> 30:49.929
OH, MY GOD.

30:49.929 --> 30:51.470
CHARLOTTE?

30:51.470 --> 30:53.812
OH, MY GOD!

30:55.144 --> 30:56.235
HOW DID YOU GET HERE?

30:56.235 --> 30:57.736
WE NEED TO GET YOU
TO A HOSPITAL.

30:57.736 --> 30:58.647
CHARLOTTE --

30:58.647 --> 30:59.648
YOUR EAR.

31:03.032 --> 31:06.075
THE NAIVE
DESERVE TWO THINGS --

31:06.075 --> 31:08.287
SWINDLING AND SCORN.

31:08.287 --> 31:10.489
THAT'S WHAT YOU ALWAYS SAY,
ISN'T IT?

31:10.489 --> 31:13.372
HOW MUCH
DO YOU HATE ME, THEN?

31:13.372 --> 31:15.624
BECAUSE I'VE BEEN
PRETTY DAMN NAIVE UNTIL NOW.

31:17.586 --> 31:18.587
[ INHALES SHAKILY ]

31:18.587 --> 31:21.090
YOU'RE TO BLAME
FOR FLIGHT 197.

31:21.090 --> 31:24.173
YOU LAUNDERED MONEY
FOR AMERICON

31:24.173 --> 31:27.506
AND THEN ARRANGED A COVER-UP
BY FRAMING DAVID CLARKE.

31:27.506 --> 31:29.848
[ Voice breaking ]
YOU EVEN SILENCED AMANDA.

31:29.848 --> 31:32.601
YOU WERE BEHIND ALL OF IT.

31:32.601 --> 31:34.683
[ SOBS QUIETLY ]

31:34.683 --> 31:38.647
CAN YOU LOOK ME IN THE EYE
AND TELL ME I'M WRONG?

31:40.479 --> 31:41.730
FINE.

31:41.730 --> 31:43.152
IF YOU DON'T HAVE
THE GUTS

31:43.152 --> 31:45.404
TO ADMIT WHAT YOU DID
TO MY REAL FATHER,

31:45.404 --> 31:46.946
I'LL TELL THE POLICE.

31:48.447 --> 31:49.868
YOU DISGUST ME.

31:51.330 --> 31:55.494
AND YOU, MY DEAR,
ARE AN UNGRATEFUL BASTARD.

31:55.494 --> 31:57.336
[ SCOFFS ]

31:59.668 --> 32:01.500
[ BREATHES SHAKILY ]

32:01.500 --> 32:04.423
MY LOVE FOR YOU
WAS SO PROFOUND

32:04.423 --> 32:06.465
THAT I WAS GONNA CONFESS
TO EVERYTHING

32:06.465 --> 32:08.007
TO SAVE YOUR LIFE.
 [ SIGHS ]

32:08.007 --> 32:09.548
YOU KNOW WHAT?
NO LONGER.

32:09.548 --> 32:10.809
NO. AND YOU'RE NOT
GOING ANYWHERE.

32:10.809 --> 32:12.391
YOU HAVE NO POWER
OVER ME!

32:12.391 --> 32:16.515
NO, I HAVE THE POWER
TO TAKE YOU OUT ANYTIME I WANT!!

32:18.477 --> 32:22.441
I HAD THE REACH TO SNUFF OUT
YOUR NUISANCE OF A SISTER.

32:23.522 --> 32:24.823
I WAS IN LEAGUE

32:24.823 --> 32:27.446
WITH A CONFEDERACY
OF GLOBAL TERRORISTS

32:27.446 --> 32:30.699
WHO TRIED TO BRING ME DOWN,
BUT I'M STILL HERE.

32:30.699 --> 32:34.623
AND YOUR FATHER, THE SELFISH
AND DIM-WITTED DAVID CLARKE --

32:34.623 --> 32:37.376
HE WAS
MY PATSY TO FREEDOM.

32:39.578 --> 32:41.130
OH, I HAVE THE POWER.

32:41.130 --> 32:44.003
AND MY SECRETS
ARE GONNA ROT INSIDE OF YOU

32:44.003 --> 32:45.504
BEYOND YOUR LAST BREATH,

32:45.504 --> 32:47.426
BECAUSE YOU ARE GONNA KEEP

32:47.426 --> 32:51.010
YOUR STUPID
AND THANKLESS MOUTH SHUT!

32:51.010 --> 32:54.893
I'M THE LAST MAN STANDING
FOR A REASON.

32:54.893 --> 32:56.855
AND IF YOU EVEN THINK
 ABOUT CROSSING ME,

32:56.855 --> 33:00.479
I WILL ERASE YOU
AS I HAVE SO MANY OTHERS.

33:04.773 --> 33:06.315
Emily:
ARE WE ON THE AIR?

33:06.315 --> 33:08.737
NOW...
 Nolan:
WE ARE BROADCASTING.

33:08.737 --> 33:10.699
...I HAVE A PRESS CONFERENCE
 TO CANCEL.

33:10.699 --> 33:12.491
CUT CHARLOTTE'S CAMERA.

33:12.491 --> 33:14.453
TURN ON THE TV
IN GRAYSON MANOR.

33:14.453 --> 33:16.075
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

33:16.075 --> 33:18.247
IF YOU EVEN THINK
 OF CROSSING ME,

33:18.247 --> 33:20.539
I WILL ERASE YOU
 AS I HAVE SO MANY OTHERS.

33:20.539 --> 33:21.790
NOW...

33:21.790 --> 33:24.543
I HAVE A PRESS CONFERENCE
 TO CANCEL.

33:25.544 --> 33:28.677
NO WORD ON HOW
 OUR SIGNAL WAS CO-OPTED,

33:28.677 --> 33:31.630
BUT IT SEEMS THE TRANSMISSION
 YOU JUST SAW WAS LIVE

33:31.630 --> 33:33.722
FROM INSIDE
 THE GRAYSON HOUSE --

33:33.722 --> 33:36.305
SHOCKING FOOTAGE
 SHOWS CONRAD GRAYSON

33:36.305 --> 33:38.937
CONFESSING TO
 A HOST OF ILLEGAL ACTIVITIES,

33:38.937 --> 33:41.100
INCLUDING TERRORISM,
 CONSPIRACY,

33:41.100 --> 33:42.601
PERJURY, AND MURDER.

33:42.601 --> 33:45.734
OUR LEGAL ANALYST
IS STANDING BY TO SHARE WITH US

33:45.734 --> 33:48.947
THE RAMIFICATIONS
 OF THESE BOMBSHELLS.

33:48.947 --> 33:52.821
[ MALE REPORTER
 SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

33:52.821 --> 33:54.413
EMS.

33:56.075 --> 33:57.656
YOU GOT HIM.

34:14.553 --> 34:16.475
[ PIANO PLAYS ]

34:25.184 --> 34:28.987
THE AUTHORITIES WILL BE
ARRIVING ANY MINUTE.

34:28.987 --> 34:32.190
I WON'T WASTE MY ENERGY
THROWING YOU OUT.

34:32.190 --> 34:33.322
THOUGH I AM SURPRISED

34:33.322 --> 34:35.324
THAT YOU HAVEN'T
GASSED UP A GULFSTREAM

34:35.324 --> 34:36.614
AND GONE ON THE LAM.

34:36.614 --> 34:39.408
OH, RUNNING WOULD BE
UNDIGNIFIED.

34:39.408 --> 34:42.161
PARTICULARLY AFTER
SUFFERING THE HUMILIATION

34:42.161 --> 34:44.623
OF BEING SOLD OUT
BY YOUR VERY OWN DAUGHTER.

34:44.623 --> 34:47.916
OH, THAT MIS-BORN WRETCH
IS YOURS ALONE.

34:47.916 --> 34:51.710
THOUGH I GATHER SHE WAS
AN UNWITTING PARTICIPANT.

34:51.710 --> 34:53.552
CHARLOTTE WAS
AS SURPRISED AS I

34:53.552 --> 34:55.214
TO DISCOVER
WE WERE BEING BROADCAST.

34:55.214 --> 34:56.594
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

34:56.594 --> 34:59.138
GIVEN YOU BOWED OUT
OF THE PRESS CONFERENCE

34:59.138 --> 35:00.429
AT THE 11th HOUR,

35:00.429 --> 35:04.603
I'M GUESSING YOU KNEW
I WAS WALKING INTO A TRAP.

35:04.603 --> 35:08.777
QUESTION IS...
DID YOU SET IT?

35:08.777 --> 35:09.988
[ CAR DOORS OPEN ]

35:09.988 --> 35:11.990
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

35:11.990 --> 35:15.534
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

35:15.534 --> 35:19.498
WELL, THERE WILL BE MANY
CONVERSATIONS WHERE I'M GOING,

35:19.498 --> 35:20.909
AND DO NOT THINK

35:20.909 --> 35:23.872
THAT I WON'T PULL
EACH SKELETON FROM YOUR CLOSET

35:23.872 --> 35:26.455
FOR THE FEDS
TO PICK OVER EVERYTHING --

35:26.455 --> 35:29.087
I MEAN,
FROM KILLING HELEN CROWLEY

35:29.087 --> 35:33.382
ALL THE WAY THROUGH TO BEING
MY NUMBER-ONE CO-CONSPIRATOR.

35:33.382 --> 35:35.093
PROVE IT.

35:35.093 --> 35:36.215
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:36.215 --> 35:38.136
WELL, AS USUAL...
[ SETS GLASS DOWN ]

35:38.136 --> 35:40.679
...I'LL HAVE OTHERS DO THAT
FOR ME.

35:40.679 --> 35:42.060
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

35:47.476 --> 35:49.648
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

35:55.073 --> 35:57.196
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

36:12.501 --> 36:15.133
GOODBYE, CONRAD.

36:15.133 --> 36:17.256
DO ROT IN HELL.

36:35.574 --> 36:37.656
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

36:49.418 --> 36:51.960
SORRY I DIDN'T
BAIL YOU OUT SOONER.

36:51.960 --> 36:53.171
WELL, YOU WERE BUSY.

36:53.171 --> 36:54.833
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:56.465 --> 36:58.257
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

36:58.257 --> 37:00.549
YOU KNOW, I NEVER EXPECTED
TO HAVE A RELATIONSHIP

37:00.549 --> 37:03.181
WITH CHARLOTTE
AFTER THIS.

37:03.181 --> 37:06.104
WELL, IF YOU'RE NOT
GONNA REVEL IN YOUR VICTORY,

37:06.104 --> 37:08.146
I WISH YOU WOULD
AT LEAST ACKNOWLEDGE IT.

37:09.268 --> 37:12.771
CONRAD WAS DEFEATED.

37:12.771 --> 37:15.023
REVENGE IS YOURS.

37:15.023 --> 37:16.775
OH, THE WAR'S NOT OVER.

37:16.775 --> 37:19.197
THERE'S STILL VICTORIA.

37:19.197 --> 37:23.201
LET HER BE
TOMORROW'S PROBLEM.

37:23.201 --> 37:25.163
TONIGHT, YOU SHOULD FOCUS
ON SOMETHING ELSE.

37:31.129 --> 37:34.423
YOU AND I --
WE'VE, UH...

37:34.423 --> 37:37.716
WE'VE CALLED IT QUITS
SO MANY TIMES.

37:37.716 --> 37:40.299
BUT WE HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO MAKE THAT STICK, REALLY,

37:40.299 --> 37:42.140
HAVE WE?

37:42.140 --> 37:45.344
AND THAT'S BECAUSE
WE FIT.

37:47.306 --> 37:49.227
WE BELONG TOGETHER.

37:57.275 --> 37:58.607
I KNOW.

38:10.459 --> 38:11.870
I NEED EMILY.

38:14.082 --> 38:15.964
JUST EMILY.

38:18.126 --> 38:19.678
HEY.

38:19.678 --> 38:23.011
HE TOLD ME
YOU TWO WERE...

38:23.011 --> 38:24.262
YOU WERE DONE.

38:24.262 --> 38:27.055
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:27.055 --> 38:29.137
WELL, IT'S COMPLICATED.

38:29.137 --> 38:30.809
NO SURPRISE THERE.

38:38.437 --> 38:41.199
YOU KNOW WHAT? IT'S --
IT'S NONE OF MY BUSINESS.

38:41.199 --> 38:42.571
I -- [ SIGHS ]

38:42.571 --> 38:46.615
IT'S GOOD TO KNOW
THAT EVERYTHING ELSE...

38:46.615 --> 38:49.287
[ CHUCKLES ]
...EVERYTHING ELSE TURNED OUT.

38:49.287 --> 38:52.210
WELL, THANKS FOR STEPPING IN
FOR AIDEN.

38:52.210 --> 38:55.624
WHEN HE ASKED ME
TO SET CHARLOTTE FREE, I...

38:55.624 --> 38:58.216
I DIDN'T UNDERSTAND HOW
THAT COULD POSSIBLY BE THE KEY

38:58.216 --> 38:59.628
TO TAKING DOWN CONRAD.

38:59.628 --> 39:02.921
ARMED WITH THE FACTS, I KNEW
THAT SHE WOULD CONFRONT HIM

39:02.921 --> 39:05.964
AND GET A CONFESSION
THAT WOULD HOLD UP IN COURT.

39:09.137 --> 39:10.389
YOU WERE THAT SURE?

39:10.389 --> 39:14.062
CHARLOTTE'S A SMART GIRL.

39:14.062 --> 39:16.685
SHE'S GOT A LOT OF FIGHT
IN HER.

39:18.186 --> 39:20.188
WE ARE BLOOD, AFTER ALL.

39:20.188 --> 39:21.820
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:21.820 --> 39:24.072
SO YOU DIDN'T REALLY...

39:24.072 --> 39:26.114
[ Chuckling ]
NEED THAT PRESS CONFERENCE?

39:26.114 --> 39:28.326
NO, I JUST NEEDED
THOSE SATELLITE TRUCKS

39:28.326 --> 39:30.078
OUTSIDE THE HOUSE.

39:32.160 --> 39:34.042
DID YOU GET TO WATCH
ANY OF IT?

39:34.042 --> 39:36.294
[ SIGHS ] EMILY, THAT'S NOT --
THAT'S NOT WHY I'M HERE.

39:36.294 --> 39:38.797
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO TELL YOU
SOMETHING SINCE YESTERDAY.

39:38.797 --> 39:39.998
CHARLOTTE RECEIVED LETTERS

39:39.998 --> 39:41.550
FROM SOMEBODY PRETENDING
TO BE DAVID CLARKE.

39:41.550 --> 39:43.001
SHE AND I TRACKED HIM
TO HIS HOUSE.

39:43.001 --> 39:44.262
THERE WAS NO ONE THERE,

39:44.262 --> 39:45.964
BUT IT WAS LIKE A SHRINE
TO YOUR FATHER.

39:45.964 --> 39:49.177
I WROTE HIM OFF
AS AN OBSESSED NUT, UNTIL...

39:54.272 --> 39:56.975
DIDN'T YOUR FATHER HAVE
SOMETHING LIKE THIS
WHEN WE WERE KIDS?

39:56.975 --> 39:58.316
I ONLY REMEMBER IT

39:58.316 --> 40:00.439
BECAUSE THERE WAS A TIME
THAT WE WERE ON THE BEACH

40:00.439 --> 40:01.860
AND --
AND YOU DROPPED IT,

40:01.860 --> 40:04.192
AND YOU MADE ME SIFT
THROUGH 60 TONS OF SAND

40:04.192 --> 40:06.234
UNTIL IT TURNED UP.

40:08.867 --> 40:10.739
EMILY?

40:10.739 --> 40:15.163
Emily:
 AN INTENTION FUELED BY PASSION
 CAN BE IMPOSSIBLE TO STOP.

40:15.163 --> 40:17.706
THIS WAS MY FATHER'S.

40:17.706 --> 40:20.168
OVER TIME, IT GAINS MOMENTUM,

40:20.168 --> 40:25.303
UNTIL IT TURNS INTO
 AN IMPETUS FOR CHANGE.

40:25.303 --> 40:27.806
HOW IS CHARLOTTE?

40:27.806 --> 40:29.678
NOT GOOD.

40:29.678 --> 40:31.219
HATING DAD.

40:31.219 --> 40:34.142
SHE'S MAD AT YOU,
 TOO.

40:34.142 --> 40:36.054
BELIEVES YOU'RE AS GUILTY
AS HE IS.

40:36.054 --> 40:37.896
THEN SHE MUST NEVER KNOW

40:37.896 --> 40:40.228
THAT I REFUSED
THE RANSOM DEMANDS.

40:42.150 --> 40:43.652
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

40:43.652 --> 40:48.487
THAT THE KIDNAPPER WANTED ME
TO CONFESS ALONGSIDE CONRAD.

40:48.487 --> 40:51.409
BUT I ACQUIRED INFORMATION TODAY
THAT MADE ME CERTAIN

40:51.409 --> 40:53.371
THAT CHARLOTTE
WOULD NEVER BE HARMED.

40:53.371 --> 40:54.623
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

40:54.623 --> 40:57.075
YOU TOOK A GAMBLE
ON YOUR OWN DAUGHTER'S LIFE?

40:57.075 --> 40:58.336
HAVE YOU LOST IT?

40:58.336 --> 41:00.248
OH, I'M VERY MUCH
IN MY RIGHT MIND

41:00.248 --> 41:02.340
ABOUT MANY THINGS.

41:04.212 --> 41:06.585
INCLUDING EMILY THORNE.

41:10.759 --> 41:15.183
THIS IS HOW A NOTION
 TRANSFORMS INTO MOTIVATION...

41:15.183 --> 41:17.185
[ CELL DOOR SLAMS ]

41:20.939 --> 41:24.272
...AND HOW A CHILD'S VOW
 BECOMES REALITY.

41:24.272 --> 41:26.815
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

41:42.290 --> 41:44.583
YOU DID THIS.

41:46.214 --> 41:47.385
YES.

41:49.257 --> 41:52.801
IN MEMORY
OF DAVID AND AMANDA CLARKE.

41:52.801 --> 41:54.092
OH.

41:56.595 --> 41:58.266
WHAT ABOUT VICTORIA?

42:00.018 --> 42:01.229
[ CHUCKLES ]

42:01.229 --> 42:03.562
OH,
I'M NOT FINISHED YET.

42:06.354 --> 42:09.067
WELL, THEN, GODSPEED.
